text: Anne Spiegel (born 15 December 1980) is a German politician of Alliance 90/The Greens. She was the Federal Minister for Family Affairs, Senior Citizens, Women and Youth in the cabinet of Chancellor Olaf Scholz from 8 December 2021 until 25 April 2022. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Rhineland-Palatinate Category:Politicians from Baden-WÃ¼rttemberg Category:Politicians of Alliance '90/The Greens Category:Family Affairs, Senior Citizens, Women and Youth ministers of Germany
